---
title: Cheesy Gochujang-Bacon Burgers with Sweet Potato Fries and Cucumber Salad
description: Messy but oh-so-good sandwich fans can count on this recipe for maximum flavor and eating satisfaction. Lean bison patties are glazed with a sweet gochujang sauce before being topped with smoky bacon, melty mozzarella and a bright quick-pickled cucumber salad. Served alongside crispy sweet potato fries and a punchy little gochujang aioli for good measure, this meal will have you coming back for seconds in no time!
